Palʊla Bob Dylan kɛ [[agoza fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 24 wiye pɩnaɣ [[1941]] [[Minesootaa|Minezotaa]] tɛtʊ taa, [[Etaazuunii|Etazuunii]] taa. Ɛ-hɩɖɛ siŋŋŋ kɔyɔ Robert Allen Zimmerman. E-hendu tewu hɩɖɛ yɔ Bob Dylan. Ɛwɛna hɩla kɩsɛsɛna ndɩ ndɩ nɛ a-taa kɔyɔ: Elston Gunnn, Blind Boy Grunt, Zimbo, Zimmy, Lucky Wilbury, Boo Wilbury, Elmer Johnson, Sergei Petrov, Jack Frost, Jack Fate, Willow Scarlet, Bob Landy, Robert Milkwood Thomas nɛ Tedham Porterhouse. 
[[Fichier:Bob_Dylan_1991.jpeg|vignette|Bob Dylan 1991]]
Ɛ-tʊma ɖɔ yem sakɩyɛ nɛ a-taa kɔyɔ: ɛkɛ kpalahʊwa lʊyʊ, wendu luɖu yaa tɩ-mayʊ, ɛkɛ ɖɔɖɔ tɔm ɖɛzɩyʊ yaa nɔɔyʊ yɔɔ aseɣɖe tɔm heyiyu, soo maɖʊ, kɛgɛdaɣ tɛ mayʊ yaa lɩzɩytʊ tʊmɩyɛ laɖʊ nɛ keɣsi maɖʊ. Bob Dylan kɛna Amerika tʊ. Pɩnzɩ 1960 taa kɛ ɛkɩla labʊ ɛ-tʊma sɔsɔna labʊ. Ete hendu natʊyʊ ɛzɩ hendu lɛɛtʊyʊ yɔ, tɩhɛzɩ ɛyaa laŋga pazɩ nɛ peyele you ŋgʊ poyowaɣ [[Fɩyɛtɩnaam]] taa nɛ ñamñam lakasɩ sakɩyɛ alɩwaatʊ ndʊ tɩ-taa yɔ.
